description: "Pure state reducer — transforms RunState given bus commands (StartRun, AdvanceRun, ApplyCommand), returns new state + effects."
files[2]{file,type,summary}:
  ReduceResult.php,readonly final class,"ReduceResult is a readonly value object that encapsulates the outcome of a reducer operation, bundling the resulting RunState and a list of side-effect instructions. It serves as a pure data container to separate computation results from their execution, ensuring immutability and clear intent in the application's event processing flow."
  RunReducer.php,final class,"The RunReducer applies domain commands to a RunState to produce a new state or reduction result, enforcing the state transition logic for agent runs. It acts as the central reducer within the application layer, coordinating state mutations based on specific command types."
